ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectNisichawayasihk Cree Nation, Mystery Lake Parcel (Manitoba) ** Creation **
PrecisOrder setting apart 1.702 hectare (4.21 acres) of land, for the use and benefit of the Nisichawayasihk Cree Nation as NCN-MYSTERY LAKE PARCEL, located within the City of Thompson, Manitoba, approximately 762 kilometres north of the City of Winnipeg, effective on the day on which Her Majesty in right of Canada becomes the registered owner of those lands.
